descriptionHTML:
Presenting "Hindu God Watch Faces" which is a unique and intelligent Smart Watch application that features beautiful watch faces with best in class User Interface for customization.
The carefully crafted design of the app syncs up your mobile and your smart watch seamlessly and provides rich user experience making it simple and easy to use.

The unique features of this Smart Watch app are:
• Watch Face can be set to change every hour
• High Quality and Beautiful images of Lord Ganesha
• Analog and Digital dials available
• High Quality and Beautiful images of various Hindu Gods (Lord Shiva, Lord Ganesha, Lord Krishna, Lord Rama, Goddess Durga, Goddess Laxmi, Goddess Santoshi Maa, Lord Hanuman etc.) are available.
